I'm asking these elders, "Please show me."Humble yourself to the elders and say, "Listen, help me. I don't have everything all figured out.

02:01:39.440 --> 02:01:59.796
You may have been through the '70s, '80s, '90s, and the early 2000s, and you've got some wisdom in you that I need."I pray for the elders to have a soft heart toward the young people and say, "Listen, you can glean it."It's their time of impartation—that is what I'm saying.

02:01:59.797 --> 02:02:13.582
But there will be a lot of them, I've seen, because of their health and certain issues, that the enemy would want them to go home early, and we don't want them going home.

02:02:13.583 --> 02:02:22.559
That's just what I see, and so I pray for these older generals. We pray for their hearts, we pray for their bodies.

02:02:22.560 --> 02:02:48.347
John Kilpatrick and these elders, pray for their health because the Lord told me John Kilpatrick would be a major voice in the end times—leaders who are not flaky in their doctrine, where you have some people with some backbone who stand for something that's good, like it was back in the revival of Brownsville.

02:02:48.348 --> 02:03:00.253
They've been through it; they lived it. They may not have done everything always right, but who has? Nobody. I don't know anybody.

02:03:00.254 --> 02:03:09.336
But at least you can learn something from their good things and their bad stuff and say, "Listen, there's something there."That's why Oral Roberts was a diamond.

02:03:09.337 --> 02:03:19.919
Look at what he did. He was a pioneer of the healing revival, went throughout the whole world, and nobody had really done it before him in this generation. He was a pioneer.

02:03:19.920 --> 02:03:27.072
And there were certain people who had the opportunity to sit with him and break bread with him, who got a glimpse of something and learned something from him.

02:03:27.073 --> 02:03:31.269
That's why I said "The Ultimate Voice"by Oral Roberts will change your life.

02:03:31.270 --> 02:03:37.939
It's one of, I think, the last books he ever wrote. And I told Diana, she reads it to me every year.

02:03:37.940 --> 02:03:46.158
Every year we read "The Ultimate Voice"by Oral Roberts, and without fail, we always read Oral Roberts at the beginning of the year.

02:03:46.159 --> 02:03:57.555
Read that book, and read it again and again, because of the wisdom that comes out of that book, it will change your life.

02:03:57.556 --> 02:04:17.919
We get books all the time from people and you go, "What life experiences do you have to write a book?"Not trying to dog your circumstance, but I like to read the books of somebody who has been through something and come out—going through the valley of the shadow of death and they didn't stay there.

02:04:17.920 --> 02:04:23.598
They may smell like a little smoke, but they have a testimony to tell about it.

02:04:23.599 --> 02:04:30.718
Give me some! Don't just write a book to write a book. You know, there's a lot of people writing books.

02:04:30.719 --> 02:04:37.649
I want something that has some oomph to it, where you have something that you imparted.

02:04:37.650 --> 02:04:53.759
You walked through some hell and you got on the other side of it, and it changed you because you didn't park your tent there and have a woe-is-me mentality. I get tired of that; I don't want to hear it.

02:04:53.760 --> 02:05:04.559
It's like people who are snot-nosed, like, "Shut up and sit down."Let's hear somebody who's been through something, who's come out not smelling, and has some integrity up in here.

02:05:04.560 --> 02:05:13.248
They don't have a scandal in their ministry where you walk away going, "That's so disappointing."Don't you get disappointed with that stuff?

02:05:13.249 --> 02:05:35.039
I know people have stuff they go through, but folks, I just want to glean from somebody who's been in ministry like Oral Roberts for 60-plus years or whatever it was, and is still standing strong on his deathbed and going home, and you go, "Wow."Or Kenneth Hagin.

02:05:35.040 --> 02:05:47.519
That's why we listen to Hagin all day today. Brother Hagin, we listen to Brother Hagin more than anything. And Kathryn Kuhlman, we listen and listen and listen to it.

02:05:47.520 --> 02:05:57.752
And you go, 'I've already...'Paisley goes, 'Daddy, I'm memorizing this.'I said, 'Yes, that's when it gets down inside of you.''I know this, Dad.'Yeah.

02:05:57.753 --> 02:06:04.677
That's when it changes you. You don't just hear it. Faith cometh by hearing and hearing and hearing and hearing.

02:06:04.678 --> 02:06:12.433
That's when it changes you. When it changes you from the inside out is how many times you've heard it over and over and over again.

02:06:12.434 --> 02:06:18.399
And I listen, Brother Hagin, I'm telling you, I've listened to some of his sermons probably, no exaggeration, 30 or 40 times.

02:06:18.400 --> 02:06:25.359
You go, 'I know what he's going to say before he says it,'but that's when it gets you.

02:06:25.360 --> 02:06:31.198
It's going to change you. So, I don't know, hopefully that helps y'all.

02:06:31.199 --> 02:06:36.500
Do they have anything else? They're asking if you saw any more things about the volcano.

02:06:36.501 --> 02:06:40.246
I haven't seen any more about the volcano. In fact, I asked the Father about the volcanoes.

02:06:40.247 --> 02:06:48.730
I said, 'Lord, you said these things are going to happen. Why do we have a lull? What happened?'A lull, lull.

02:06:48.731 --> 02:06:55.546
It seems like it was escalating, escalating, escalating, and then it gets deflated like a balloon. Isn't it interesting?

02:06:55.547 --> 02:07:09.616
To me, when you pray into it and you see it, and the volcanoes and the earthquakes are happening all out there in the Ring of Fire, and it happened like all the time, and then all of a sudden it went—and I'm like, is that our prayers or are you waiting?

02:07:09.617 --> 02:07:19.925
I feel something is about to happen, and He's waiting. How does the UN handle Israel in the next week or two weeks?

02:07:19.926 --> 02:07:23.593
What's going to happen with the rest of this month, a September to remember?

02:07:23.595 --> 02:07:29.493
What are we looking at? What I saw from the fifth on, with the fog over it with a circle around it.

02:07:29.494 --> 02:07:33.439
Why? What? What's going on with that? We're praying into that.

02:07:33.440 --> 02:07:39.055
Something is about to happen where everything will change within a 24-hour period.

02:07:39.056 --> 02:07:50.238
A major shaking, a point of no return in the spirit realm. And I believe it has to do with the 23rd.

02:07:50.239 --> 02:07:55.596
What are you looking at? They're all asking about the thousand years and then it's all coming.

02:07:55.597 --> 02:08:06.076
The thousand years. Oh, it's so beautiful. I never talk about it because I don't have scripture to back it, so I don't ever...

02:08:06.077 --> 02:08:12.876
I know I talk about a lot of this other stuff, but when it comes to biblical stuff, I try not to touch things because people get real ticked off.

02:08:12.877 --> 02:08:19.447
