02:08:19.448 --> 02:08:25.285
I can back up both of why they believe it's flat earth and why I believe it's a round earth.

02:08:25.286 --> 02:08:33.601
When I went to heaven and I saw it as I was leaving, it's a massive ball. It's a massive planet.

02:08:33.602 --> 02:08:38.891
Now, I'm just telling you what I saw, but there's no darkness; it's completely light.

02:08:38.892 --> 02:08:52.051
But it's tucked away in the universe as a ripple. I can see it. I'll tell y'all. I'll tell you some things.

02:08:52.052 --> 02:09:00.156
You go, 'Well, I don't know about that.'Well, whatever you ask. It's tucked away.

02:09:00.157 --> 02:09:11.017
