02:09:11.018 --> 02:09:23.696
It's movable. And the planet heaven is a massive ball, a massive planet, and it is huge, bigger than Jupiter, huge.

02:09:23.697 --> 02:09:37.602
And I could see it hidden in a dimension all around, and the glory from God's glory was shining, and the whole place was glowing.

02:09:37.603 --> 02:09:46.590
There's no darkness. There's no darkness, but it's all split up, and you can see the land and you can see everything.

02:09:46.591 --> 02:09:52.677
And I'm telling you, it's way out there. But this is what I saw, and it's glorious.

02:09:52.678 --> 02:09:56.799
Every time they go there, people are going to something, right?

02:09:56.800 --> 02:10:00.699
And you see it when you get there. But I'm talking about as you're there.

02:10:00.700 --> 02:10:08.959
It's an actual 'as earth as it is in heaven'place. It's an actual place.

02:10:08.960 --> 02:10:11.811
I know it may be controversial, but I'm just telling you what I saw.

02:10:11.812 --> 02:10:19.037
It's an actual place, and it's beautiful. And everything in heaven is gorgeous.

02:10:19.038 --> 02:10:26.179
Even the horses, even the bridles on the horses, even everything.

02:10:26.180 --> 02:10:43.352
Everything is beautiful and spectacularly made, created for pleasure and glory for you, and love for you—everything: the plates, the mugs, everything, the trees, the flowers.

02:10:43.353 --> 02:10:52.319
