02:11:08.233 --> 02:11:14.128
I don't know, I'm heavy because I want to eat everything, but I'm just saying everything to me looks edible.

02:11:14.129 --> 02:11:21.635
Like, look at that, you could eat that. It's a flower. I'm sorry, it's not funny, but it is. But that's how beautiful it looks like.

02:11:21.636 --> 02:11:30.271
Oh my goodness, you look like you could bite that, like take that and put that in your mouth. But that's how beautiful it was.

02:11:30.273 --> 02:11:43.919
As I see these things and the Lord allows me, as I saw Lucy and them praying at the chairs, everything is so gorgeous looking through the tunnels. I've seen so much. The Lord has allowed me to see.

02:11:43.920 --> 02:12:01.370
But on the thousand years, I'll tell you this: where Jesus stays, where His temple is, the columns of this thing are amazing, all of the steps going up to it, and the robes on the people.

02:12:01.371 --> 02:12:20.638
Okay, every one of you will be rewarded for what you did on this earth and what you do on this earth, for the rewards that are displayed upon your robes.

02:12:20.639 --> 02:12:36.959
