02:15:22.636 --> 02:15:43.285
But I saw an insignia, like a tattoo, saying it was on you, of what one was like—like when you see a Purple Heart for somebody who got wounded in war here in America, you have a Purple Heart.

02:15:43.286 --> 02:15:55.118
That's the kind of purple that was on some of these medals. It was beautiful gold, and they were like a crest, a royal crest.

02:15:55.119 --> 02:16:06.638
Some of them were bronze, some of them were gold, some of them were silver, but each one of them had something to do with what you were called to do in the thousand years.

02:16:06.639 --> 02:16:13.000
